---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { REPLY_EMAIL } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <article class="page">
    <h1 class="font-display">About</h1>
    <p>
      I write here about machine learning, language models, and statistics —
      slowly, and mostly to find out what I actually think.
    </p>
    <p>
      By day I work close to these systems; the rest of the time I read papers,
      run small experiments, and explain ideas to myself until they hold still.
      This site is where some of that lands, once it has steeped long enough to
      be worth keeping.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'd rather be slow and right than fast and loud, so there are no comments,
      no view counts, and nothing here is on a schedule. If a piece is wrong, or
      you want to push back on it, <a href={`mailto:${REPLY_EMAIL}`}>reply by
      email</a> — I read everything.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
